Create a Timer

Requirements
1. Hour, Mins and Secs field
    a. This field should be editable for user to enter and remove values(only numbers are accepted => 2 digit)
    b. Should not be editable once the user has started the Timer
    c. The timer value entered should be saved and used on RESET done by user

2. there should be START, PAUSE, RESET AND CANCEL/REFRESH button in the application
    a. Only start button should be there when until the user enters the values and start the timer
    b. once the timer the started the 3 other buttons should be visible.


What Should be done??

* a function to accept timer value from user and set the timer value 
* a function to evoke the timer and decrease value every sec 
